dct_description_sm: Benjamin Peirce Superintendent ; compiled and drawn by A. Lindenkohl ; Verified J. E. Hilgard Assist. Coast Survey in charge of Office.
Relief shown by hachures and shading; depths by bathymetric soundings.
2 bar scales on map, given in "Statute Miles" and "Nautical Miles."
Shows topography, drainage, tides, light houses, anchorage points.
Includes index indicating materials: mud, sand, gravel, shells.
"Electrotype Copy No. 1 by G. Mathiot U.S.C.S." at top right.
